Ujef9ZtWgLaMEx5u1jVK8v6ZO8nEwmV8MJVS0c\/s1600\/foto.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\u003E\u003Cimg border=\"0\" height=\"233\" src=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEh5mG1-qsp_BHlmqcndoQ5x5EMty90KZ23FDyQmk_xzP09bE-E0YvjIlJJaA5PETjuoOfMIEEj__5BjQbniPvViEQ1Q9zZLaDVeP6l_EUjef9ZtWgLaMEx5u1jVK8v6ZO8nEwmV8MJVS0c\/s1600\/foto.jpg\" width=\"320\" \/\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/td\u003E\u003C\/tr\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003EV zimnom období sú na hradisku viditeľné valy on Nimnice aj napriek hustému porastu\u003C\/td\u003E\u003C\/tr\u003E\n\u003C\/tbody\u003E\u003C\/table\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003E\nLetecké zábery hradiska (Stanka F.):\u003Cbr \/\u003E\n\u003Cbr \/\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEh7uTIEhX_vITU1wqTb2E51m6rdL7J2yo8vz6Mv_XBvASHU6uB4EBvm_-OrK29h4auooX7LvmvjOo-dW9JOxH1Kei1-UNCerL8JiINzSl7ztuzojNdurTxFYLLtfIKVjjxsFg62apRKIZI\/s1600\/let01.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"\u003E\u003Cimg border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEh7uTIEhX_vITU1wqTb2E51m6rdL7J2yo8vz6Mv_XBvASHU6uB4EBvm_-OrK29h4auooX7LvmvjOo-dW9JOxH1Kei1-UNCerL8JiINzSl7ztuzojNdurTxFYLLtfIKVjjxsFg62apRKIZI\/s1600\/let01.jpg\" width=\"320\" \/\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cbr \/\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/blogger.googleusercontent.com\/img\/b\/R29vZ2xl\/AVvXsEg_wDWGO5QkKXAfm49hcq2IaG8ieYgDOTFDAny0C2asVKHzDIc__odHOaKaYj8-oxpTfcbZqA1ScFhsILqBbHvm4ZqxW4JDDjo_o5ccA2U87nRz2mJXYU0XP28-nL3q4yvyTNdsOMprrAo\/s1600\/let12.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"\u003E\u003Cimg border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src